Uttar Pradesh
Nov 05, 2014
Abuse
Description:
			A woman allegedly committed suicide by setting herself ablaze over a family dispute in Bhandora village of the district.

Sonam was married to Armesh, who used to beat her every day after drinking. Upset over the thrashings, she took the extreme step yesterday.

The body was cremated without informing the police by the woman's in-laws.

Police is investigating the matter.


